| Performance | 5/10 | C |
| Feature Completeness | 8/10 | B+ |
| **Overall** | **6.4/10** | **C+** |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The system has **excellent domain coverage** and **strong business logic** (especially accounting double-entry and POS flow). However, it has **critical security gaps** (RBAC not enforced, missing tenant isolation on child tables, no rate limiting) that MUST be addressed before production deployment. The recommended Phase 1 security hardening should be treated as a **blocking prerequisite** for any production launch.
